{"tid":1266901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我會記得這年代裡你做的事情","createTime":"2019-06-29T16:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T17:05:41.000Z","uid":600,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"47ea1683da175ad2439df03a3a75afd2eecddc67","tid":1266901,"uid":600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:18:49.000Z","msg":"代朋友開post<br />\n<br />\n作為一個八十後<br />\n做到嘅事可能好微小<br />\n我哋只係想話比香港人知<br />\n其實有好多人好愛香港<br />\n仲有好多人係支持住下一代<br />\n無論喺呢個時候幾咁失望<br />\n我地都唔可以絕望<br />\n<br />\n我同designer朋友好想話比大家知<br />\n五個人唔等於暴徒<br />\n無人係暴徒！<br />\n我地每個人都係捍衛香港嘅戰士<br />\n各自用自己方法保護香港嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vNosEFi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvNosEFi.png&h=5a5c135c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ohxJc0j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FohxJc0j.png&h=e5f1fb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KjnAOyF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKjnAOyF.png&h=18e85752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W5r6aM0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW5r6aM0.png&h=ec28c5f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZUWRmTG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUWRmTG.png&h=8974aa8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋會少量印刷呢啲貼紙喺七一遊行派發<br />\n希望更多人知道，每個崗位嘅人都一直撐住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n七一到時見<br />\n一個都不能少！"},{"pid":"35706db90ad90101c9194193cd30dad565e10ec0","tid":1266901,"uid":5680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:20:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q-kGIHSHLl0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQ-kGIHSHLl0&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=550b0dd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Q-kGIHSHLl0</a>"},{"pid":"43af715b4365f19bff2eb9a9d11a1d3ea03fe2da","tid":1266901,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:20:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a45992d038d860c04de0288bbda5cf899f74ab82","tid":1266901,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:22:41.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9f4a205a7383e861f29713e963d112ae03b8eb","tid":1266901,"uid":87062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:25:39.000Z","msg":"好靚"},{"pid":"697cd30efeec7c2f4b96e86688a5206c8fe3fde8","tid":1266901,"uid":600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dRiXhyu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdRiXhyu.png&h=d982fac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己post自己推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2c8e578de4bb5b31885adb1f9eb8d209be8622","tid":1266901,"uid":595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d63cfbd58089e2f490c7acdd175daea4402664","tid":1266901,"uid":7534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:39:16.000Z","msg":"Pish 多謝你有心又出錢出力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6e53d2c23b2723759008c196eb1add095f2eea","tid":1266901,"uid":225144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:39:37.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一開吹水區，已經見到無數既post都係關於想尋死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n各位巴絲真係唔好諗咁多呀，我同大家一樣都好失落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n如果你地真係好頂唔順既，不如入來呢個tg gp，我<br />\n地一齊面對啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/KVqQTxPKuulibHHUoGW-Dg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FKVqQTxPKuulibHHUoGW-Dg&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo5KGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=f9efbabe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/KVqQTxPKuulibHHUoGW-Dg</a>"},{"pid":"d77fd3b6bba59792337d8bf30c638c2050dab74a","tid":1266901,"uid":2256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:42:31.000Z","msg":"你在曾經不僅是你自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n還有二百萬香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f37ce8eb38605d7588f1b2a6297934fabf3a7fd","tid":1266901,"uid":600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83d63cfbd58089e2f490c7acdd175daea4402664","tid":1266901,"uid":7534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:39:16.000Z","msg":"Pish 多謝你有心又出錢出力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:49:50.000Z","msg":"代朋友多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都只係為自己所愛嘅地方略盡綿力<br />\n咁微不足道嘅行為都唔算得係咩<br />\n大家收到份心意keep住團火繼續撐落去就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2fdf6bf21bc5c7f59011b9ab0745982f71597a8","tid":1266901,"uid":600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d77fd3b6bba59792337d8bf30c638c2050dab74a","tid":1266901,"uid":2256,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:42:31.000Z","msg":"你在曾經不僅是你自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n還有二百萬香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:50:59.000Z","msg":"你走出千萬人群獨行<br />\n往柳暗花明山窮水盡去"},{"pi